-- Sri Lanka's Seylan Bank Reports First-Half Net Income More Than Doubles
-- Anusha Ondaatjie
-- 2010-07-30T01:42:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/sri-lanka-s-seylan-bank-s-reports-first-half-net-income-more-than-doubles.html

          
          
             Seylan Bank Plc., a Colombo-based
lender, posted profit of 507 million rupees ($4.5 million) in
the first half ended June 30, compared with 188 million rupees a
year earlier, according to a statement to the Colombo Stock
Exchange.  
